---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Story - TORVIX Toronto">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="flex-grow pt-32 lg:pt-40 min-h-screen bg-[#f9f8f6]">
    
    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center reveal">
        <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 mb-6 text-xs font-sans tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-500 border border-slate-300">
          Toronto, Canada
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          Architectural Vision.<br/>
          <span class="italic font-light">Structural Integrity.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed tracking-wide font-sans">
          TORVIX is a premier design-build firm founded on a singular belief: that breathtaking design is hollow without flawless execution. 
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 lg:py-40 bg-white border-y border-slate-200">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
          <div class="reveal delay-100">
            <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-10 tracking-tight leading-[1.2]">
              The Master Craftsmen Behind the Walls.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-8 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-sans tracking-wide text-lg">
              <p>
                Our reputation is built by the hands of our master craftsmen. From our structural engineers to our finishing carpenters and tile masons, every member of the TORVIX team shares an obsessive dedication to precision.
              </p>
              <p>
                We do not view construction merely as an assembly of materials. We approach it as the careful, deliberate execution of an architectural vision. We specialize in marrying high-end aesthetics with enduring structural integrity, ensuring that what happens behind the drywall is just as beautiful as the final layer of paint.
              </p>
              <p>
                Based in Toronto, our firm brings discipline, politeness, and absolute professionalism to every job site, ensuring that the process of building your dream home is as refined as the home itself.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal delay-200">
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden border border-slate-200 rounded-none bg-slate-100 aspect-[4/5] p-2">
              <img 
                src="/images/projects/Ready pics_/webp_cikti/img_4978.webp" 
                alt="Architectural Framing Toronto" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-90 rounded-none hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-700"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
